<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='486' id='t-486'>I love paper, and I love technology,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='4570' id='t-4570'>and what I do is I make paper interactive.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='7901' id='t-7901'>And that's what I say when
