<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='14432' id='t-14432'>is to take the technology and be creative</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='17444' id='t-17444'>and create experiences.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='19545' id='t-19545'>So I tried to think
