<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='23917' id='t-23917'>that I wanted to print two DJ decks</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='27730' id='t-27730'>and to try and mix some music.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='30214' id='t-30214'>And I'm going to try
and show that at the end,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='32429' id='t-32429'>and the suspense will be
as much mine if it works.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='35938' id='t-35938'>And I'm not a DJ, and I'm not a musician,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='38604' id='t-38604'>so I'm a little bit scared of that.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='41327' id='t-41327'>So I think, I found the best
