<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='52896' id='t-52896'>and I'll just describe those first,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='54587' id='t-54587'>and then talk about some of my work.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='56606' id='t-56606'>So when I was a kid,
I was obsessed with wires,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='59835' id='t-59835'>and I used to thread them under my carpet</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='62941' id='t-62941'>and thread them behind the walls</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='64535' id='t-64535'>and have little switches
