<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='66856' id='t-66856'>and I wanted to make
my bedroom be interactive</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='69572' id='t-69572'>but kind of all hidden away.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='71102' id='t-71102'>And I was also really
interested in wireless as well.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='75143' id='t-75143'>So I bought one of those
