<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='123344' id='t-123344'>I ended up on a farm
in the middle of nowhere.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='127326' id='t-127326'>It was in far western New South Wales.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='129774' id='t-129774'>And this farm was 120,000 acres.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='132525' id='t-132525'>There were 22,000 sheep,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='134318' id='t-134318'>and it was about 40 degrees,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='136232' id='t-136232'>or 100 or so Fahrenheit.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='138886' id='t-138886'>And on this farm there
was the farmer, his wife,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='141920' id='t-141920'>and there was the four-year-old daughter.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='144631' id='t-144631'>And they kind of took me into the farm</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='147253' id='t-147253'>and showed me what it
