<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='159149' id='t-159149'>And we'd do that by building fences,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='161140' id='t-161140'>using motorbikes and horses,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='163694' id='t-163694'>and the sheep would make
