<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='169954' id='t-169954'>And what I learned was,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='171862' id='t-171862'>although at the time, like everyone else,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='173958' id='t-173958'>I thought sheep were pretty stupid</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='175602' id='t-175602'>because they didn't do
