<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='177310' id='t-177310'>what I realize now, probably
only just in the last few weeks</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='180431' id='t-180431'>looking back, is the sheep
weren't stupid at all.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='182462' id='t-182462'>We'd put them in an environment
where they didn't want to be,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='184894' id='t-184894'>and they didn't want to do
what we wanted them to do.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='187442' id='t-187442'>So the challenge was to try and get them</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='189856' id='t-189856'>to do what we wanted them to do</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='190878' id='t-190878'>by listening to the weather,
the lay of the land,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='193969' id='t-193969'>and creating things
