<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='196980' id='t-196980'>and go where we wanted them to go.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='199678' id='t-199678'>Another bunch of years later,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='201285' id='t-201285'>I ended up at Cambridge University</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='203644' id='t-203644'>at the Cavendish Laboratory in the U.K.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='205826' id='t-205826'>doing a Ph.D. in physics.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='207540' id='t-207540'>My Ph.D. was to move electrons
around, one at a time.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='212564' id='t-212564'>And I realize — again, it's kind
of these realizations</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='215220' id='t-215220'>looking back as to what I did —</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='217419' id='t-217419'>I realize now that it
