<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='220350' id='t-220350'>as moving sheep around.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='222187' id='t-222187'>It really is.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='224461' id='t-224461'>It's just you do it
