<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='306128' id='t-306128'>When I spoke to some printers
when I started doing this</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='308249' id='t-308249'>and told them what I wanted to do,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='309893' id='t-309893'>which was to print
