<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='312119' id='t-312119'>they told me it couldn't be done,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='313715' id='t-313715'>again, that kind of favorite thing.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='315961' id='t-315961'>So I got about 10 credit cards and loans</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='320667' id='t-320667'>and got myself very close
